    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"Open Source Projects\"\npagetitle: \"Projects | Anthony Faustine\"\ndescription-meta: \"Open-source ML libraries for forecasting, load monitoring, and production machine learning systems.\"\n\nformat:\n  html:\n    page-layout: full\n    body-class: \"projects-page\"\n\ntoc: false\n---\n\n<div class=\"projects-header\">\n\n<p>Production-grade ML libraries from research to enterprise</p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"projects-timeline\">\n\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"timeline-event timeline-event--active delay-3s animated fadeInUp\">\n      <div class=\"timeline-icon\">\n        <i class=\"bi bi-rocket\"></i>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"timeline-date\">\n        2024\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"timeline-content\">\n        <div class=\"timeline-title\">\n          Twiga\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-description\">\n          <p>Production forecasting library with REST-serving, MLOps, and hyperparameter optimization.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-meta\">\n          <span class=\"timeline-status\"><i class=\"bi bi-lightning-fill\"></i> Active</span>\n          <span>Updated: 2024-06</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-links\">\n          <a href=\"https://pypi.org/project/twiga/\" class=\"timeline-link\" title=\"PyPI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><i class=\"bi bi-box-seam\"></i>PyPI</a>\n<a href=\"https://sambaiga.github.io/twiga-docs/\" class=\"timeline-link\" title=\"Documentation\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><i class=\"bi bi-book\"></i>Documentation</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/sambaiga/twiga\" class=\"timeline-link\" title=\"GitHub\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><i class=\"bi bi-github\"></i>GitHub</a>\n\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"timeline-event timeline-event--active delay-2s animated fadeInUp\">\n      <div class=\"timeline-icon\">\n        <i class=\"bi bi-rocket\"></i>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"timeline-date\">\n        2023\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"timeline-content\">\n        <div class=\"timeline-title\">\n          MLPForecast\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-description\">\n          <p>MLP-based net-load forecasting with uncertainty quantification for distribution networks.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-meta\">\n          <span class=\"timeline-status\"><i class=\"bi bi-lightning-fill\"></i> Active</span>\n          <span>Updated: 2024-03</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-links\">\n          <a href=\"https://github.com/sambaiga/mlpforecast\" class=\"timeline-link\" title=\"GitHub\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><i class=\"bi bi-github\"></i>GitHub</a>\n<a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1109/TPWRS.2024.3400123\" class=\"timeline-link\" title=\"View Paper\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><i class=\"bi bi-file-pdf\"></i>Paper</a>\n\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"timeline-event timeline-event--maintained delay-1s animated fadeInUp\">\n      <div class=\"timeline-icon\">\n        <i class=\"bi bi-gear\"></i>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"timeline-date\">\n        2023\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"timeline-content\">\n        <div class=\"timeline-title\">\n          MLCFCD\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-description\">\n          <p>Machine learning-based conformal forecasting with probabilistic predictions and coverage guarantees.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-meta\">\n          <span class=\"timeline-status\"><i class=\"bi bi-shield-check\"></i> Maintained</span>\n          <span>Updated: 2023-12</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-links\">\n          <a href=\"https://github.com/sambaiga/MLCFCD\" class=\"timeline-link\" title=\"GitHub\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><i class=\"bi bi-github\"></i>GitHub</a>\n\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"timeline-event timeline-event--maintained  animated fadeInUp\">\n      <div class=\"timeline-icon\">\n        <i class=\"bi bi-gear\"></i>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"timeline-date\">\n        2021\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"timeline-content\">\n        <div class=\"timeline-title\">\n          AWRGNILM\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-description\">\n          <p>Adaptive weighted recurrence graphs for appliance recognition in non-intrusive load monitoring.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-meta\">\n          <span class=\"timeline-status\"><i class=\"bi bi-shield-check\"></i> Maintained</span>\n          <span>Updated: 2021-12</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-links\">\n          <a href=\"https://github.com/sambaiga/AWRGNILM\" class=\"timeline-link\" title=\"GitHub\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><i class=\"bi bi-github\"></i>GitHub</a>\n<a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1109/TSG.2020.3010621\" class=\"timeline-link\" title=\"View Paper\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><i class=\"bi bi-file-pdf\"></i>Paper</a>\n\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"timeline-event timeline-event--community  animated fadeInUp\">\n      <div class=\"timeline-icon\">\n        <i class=\"bi bi-people\"></i>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"timeline-date\">\n        2020\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"timeline-content\">\n        <div class=\"timeline-title\">\n          Deep-NILMtk\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-description\">\n          <p>Community-driven deep learning toolkit for NILM with automation, hyperparameters, and modular pipelines.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-meta\">\n          <span class=\"timeline-status\"><i class=\"bi bi-globe\"></i> Community</span>\n          <span>Updated: 2023-06</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-links\">\n          <a href=\"https://github.com/BHafsa/Deep-NILMtk\" class=\"timeline-link\" title=\"GitHub\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><i class=\"bi bi-github\"></i>GitHub</a>\n<a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1109/TII.2022.3206322\" class=\"timeline-link\" title=\"View Paper\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><i class=\"bi bi-file-pdf\"></i>Paper</a>\n\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n```\n\n</div>\n\n---\n\n## Contributing\n\nThese projects welcome contributions and collaboration.\n\n[Open an Issue](https://github.com/sambaiga){.btn .btn-outline-primary .btn-sm} [Submit a PR](https://github.com/sambaiga){.btn .btn-outline-primary .btn-sm}\n",
